# Logs / scratch
*.log
/tmp/
chess_mcp_implementation_plan.md

# Local game history + coaching profiles (CHESS_DATA_DIR; never commit personal game data)
.chess-review/

# Update sentinel written by the in-app "Update now" button; consumed by the launcher on next start.
.update-requested
# Transient backup dirs created by scripts/apply_update.py during an atomic copy (removed on success).
.update-backup-*

# Built macOS app bundle (scripts/build_app.sh; only the script is committed)
*.app/
